{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c1cdff4fd4","title":"关于朱德、荣臻访问民主德国、苏联时应注意事项的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cdd3858e92","index":0,"year":1955,"month":11,"day":28,"articleId":"c1cdff4fd4"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"a7ea3bd8ce","name":"朱德","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"80ece58e11","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c1cdff4fd4","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"爱荣臻，当时任中共中央军委委员、全国人大常委会委员、国防委员会副主席。"},{"id":"58e4463bef","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c1cdff4fd4","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在国务院副总理兼国防部部长彭德怀1955年11月26日给毛泽东的报告上。报告中说，最近德意志民主共和国副总理施托夫来信，提出向中国供应光学、医疗等仪器问题，看来信意思，可能是为这些产品在中国找市场。"},{"id":"e2c1216920","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c1cdff4fd4","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。朱，指朱德。陈，指陈云，当时任中共中央书记处书记、国务院副总理。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央秘书长、国务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6b736e0cfd","type":"title","text":"关于朱德、鼓荣臻访向民主德国、苏联时应注意事项的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c1cdff4fd4"},{"id":"80ece58e11","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、朱、陈、邓、慧荣臻阅，退毛。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c1cdff4fd4"},{"id":"58e4463bef","type":"paragraph","text":"朱德同志和慧荣臻同志去德、苏，在谈话时请加注意，不要涉及具体事项的承诺，如对方涉及，应推出两国外交部和对外贸易部去商谈。此件所说情况，值得注意。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c1cdff4fd4"},{"id":"e2c1216920","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c1cdff4fd4"},{"id":"bcf8e38cf9","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月廿八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"c1cdff4fd4"}],"p